productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on powerviolence radio, decided to give it a try.
This turquoise works really well. It sympathetically improves my baseball by a lot.
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
I saw one of these in Bhutan and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
